results.name: Number of times that Fibonacci(n)-Fibonacci(i) is prime for i=0..n-3.
comment: We exclude i=n-2 and i=n-1 because they yield Fibonacci(n-2) and Fibonacci(n-1), respectively. Sequence A113190 lists the n for which a(n)=0.
xref: Cf. A113188 (primes that are the difference of two Fibonacci numbers).
results.author: _T. D. Noe_, Oct 17 2005
